---
---

<html lang="es">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Rekval Global | Gestión Patrimonial 360°</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="container nav">
        <div class="logo">REKVAL</div>

        <nav>
          <a href="#">Inicio</a>
          <a href="#">Nosotros</a>
          <a href="#">Servicios</a>
          <a href="#">Cómo trabajamos</a>
          <a href="#">Contacto</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-grid">
          <div class="hero-content">
            <span class="eyebrow">Gestión Patrimonial 360°</span>

            <h1>Protegemos, ordenamos y proyectamos tu patrimonio.</h1>

            <p>
              En Rekval Global acompañamos a personas, familias y empresas en la
              planificación, protección y crecimiento de su patrimonio con una mirada
              estratégica, cercana y de largo plazo.
            </p>

            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a class="btn primary" href="#">Conversemos</a>
              <a class="btn secondary" href="#">Ver servicios</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-card">
            <p>Planificación</p>
            <p>Inversión</p>
            <p>Protección</p>
            <p>Sucesión</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

<style>
  :global(*) {
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  :global(body) {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    background: #07111f;
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .container {
    width: min(1120px, 92%);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .site-header {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    width: 100%;
    z-index: 10;
    padding: 24px 0;
    background: rgba(7, 17, 31, 0.72);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
  }

  .nav {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  }

  nav {
    display: flex;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  nav a {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  nav a:hover {
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 140px 0 80px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 20%, rgba(55, 112, 145, 0.45), transparent 34%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #07111f 0%, #0c1e32 48%, #122c42 100%);
  }

  .hero-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.2fr 0.8fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 64px;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: #8fd3ff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  h1 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(42px, 6vw, 78px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: -0.06em;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 28px 0 0;
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    margin-top: 36px;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    min-height: 48px;
    padding: 0 24px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-weight: 700;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .primary {
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #07111f;
  }

  .secondary {
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.26);
    color: #ffffff;
  }

  .hero-card {
    padding: 34px;
    border-radius: 28px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
  }

  .hero-card p {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 22px 0;
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  }

  .hero-card p:last-child {
    border-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    nav {
      display: none;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .hero {
      padding-top: 120px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
  }
</style>